item.title: Hello, this is Emma.
item.description: I am a trans, lesbian, polyamorous, veteran, Asian woman. I currently work as a software engineer in Chicago. It’s kind of a long story how I got here (long story to be found in blog posts). The tl;dr version. My egg cracked on Halloween 2019, while I was living in Tokyo with my wife thanks to a very euphoric crossplay (2B from Nier: Automata). A month later, I came out and started transitioning.
